snippet.title: 2019 Proton Saga 1.3 Premium facelift Review, Best Car to Buy under RM40,000!
snippet.description:
The Proton Saga was given a facelift in 2019 and it underwent some big changes thanks to Proton-Geely partnership.

Much of the changes are under the skin, most notably the new 4-speed automatic transmission that replaces the Punch CVT. Let Adrian show you some of the intricate details that you might have missed in the Proton Saga Facelift.
_____________________________________________

Quick Specs:
Name: 2019 Proton Saga 1.3 Premium Facelift
Engine: 1.3-litre 4-cylinder VVT petrol
Power: 95 PS & 120 Nm
Transmission: 4-speed automatic
0 - 100 km/h: 14.6 seconds (as tested)
Top Speed: N/A
Price: RM 39,800 (OTR without insurance)

Read More:  https://www.wapcar.my/cars/proton/saga
